OL,3,CRedundancies made at Lindsey oil
OL,4,Crefinery as bids considered for the
OL,5,Csite
OL,7,FOver a hundred redundancies have been
OL,8,Fannounced at a major oil refinery in
OL,9,FLincolnshire, even though there are at
OL,10,Fleast two bids to buy and operate the
OL,11,Fsite, say Unite.
OL,13,FFTI, the insolvency firm running
OL,14,FLindsey oil refinery will be cutting
OL,15,F125 jobs, with 255 employees retaining
OL,16,Ftheir positions.
OL,18,FLindsey supports 420 directly employed
OL,19,Fworkers plus a further 500 contract
OL,20,Fjobs and potentially thousands in the
OL,21,Fsupply chain.
