OL,5,Csite
OL,7,FPrax, the owner's of the refinery,
OL,8,Fclaim the decision was not taken
OL,9,Flightly and follows a thorough review
OL,10,Fof all aspects of the business,
OL,11,Ffollowing its insolvency.
OL,13,FA spokesperson for the company said:
OL,14,F"We understand that this a very
OL,15,Fdifficult time for all those affected
OL,16,Fby this decision, and the Insolvency
OL,17,FService will fully support employees
OL,18,Fsubject to redundancy via the
OL,19,FRedundancy Payments Service.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
