OL,5,Csite
OL,7,FThe union believes that the insolvency
OL,8,Ffirm FTI's preferred bidder wishes to
OL,9,Fmothball the site and use it as a
OL,10,Fstorage terminal for oil tankers.
OL,12,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,13,Fsaid: "The government has been tin
OL,14,Feared to the plight of workers at the
OL,15,Fsecond oil refinery facing closure in
OL,16,Fless than a year. This makes a mockery
OL,17,Fof government promises to protect
OL,18,Fworkers and its plan for net zero.
OL,26,@uD@GOU
