OL,5,Csite
OL,7,FHe said: "The Official Receiver has
OL,8,Fmade this independent decision now in
OL,9,Forder to provide employees with as
OL,10,Fmuch notice as possible, while
OL,11,Fconcluding the sales process in the
OL,12,Fcoming weeks. The majority of the
OL,13,Fworkforce will be retained beyond the
OL,14,Fend of October and we remain hopeful
OL,15,Fthat a solution will be found that
OL,16,Fsupports jobs on the site long-term.
OL,26,@oD@JOU
