OL,7,F"The Official Receiver is
OL,8,Findependently assessing potential bids
OL,9,Ffor the future of the refinery and its
OL,10,Fassets and has made clear he will
OL,11,Fcontinue to work with all bidders with
OL,12,Fcredible and deliverable proposals."
OL,14,FThe government says it will take
OL,15,Fimmediate action to fund a Training
OL,16,FGuarantee for refinery workers to
OL,17,Fsupport them to find new, secure, long-
OL,18,Fterm jobs, including in the growing
OL,19,Fclean energy workforce.
